晠字的基本解释

晠
shèng
古同“晟”，光明。
古同“盛”，盛大。

晠字的汉语字典释义

[①]［shèng］
［《廣韻》承正切，去勁，禪。］
亦作“晠1”。
(1)旺盛；兴盛；茂盛。
(2)众多；丰盛。
(3)谓使丰足。
(4)大；盛大。
(5)为深重。
(6)华美。
(7)极；甚。
(8)盛行。
(9)抚育。参见“盛養”。
(10)称赞。
(11)姓。
[②]［chéng］
［《廣韻》是征切，平清，禪。］
(1)以器装物。
(2)受物之器。
(3)祭祀时放在容器中的黍稷等祭品。
(4)容纳；承受。
(5)指居住。
(6)通“成”。
(7)通“郕”。

晠字的康熙字典解释

【辰集上】【日字部】　晠； 康熙笔画：11； 页码：页496第01
【集韻】晟或書作晠。

晠
Chinese dictionary definition of words
[①]［shèng］
["Guangyun" inherits the tangent, goes for energy, and Zen. ]
Also known as "Yi 1".
(1) Exuberant; prosperous; luxuriant.
(2) Numerous; abundant.
(3) That is to make abundance.
(4) Big; grand.
(5) is profound.
(6) Gorgeous.
(7) Extremely; Very.
(8) Prevailing.
(9) Upbringing. See "Prosperity."
(10) Compliment.
(11) Last name.
[②]［chéng］
["Guangyun" is Zhengqie, Pingqing, and Zen. ]
(1) Install objects with utensils.
(2) Object-receiving device.
(3) Sacrifices such as millet placed in a container at the time of sacrifice.
(4) To accommodate; to bear.
(5) Refers to residence.
(6) Link "成".
(7) Through "郕".
